Spider Foot
https://www.spiderfoot.net/
SpiderFoot automates OSINT to find everything possible about your target.
Recon by Secapps
https://secapps.com/market/recon
Recon is a state of the art information gathering and target reconnaissance tool built on top of a powerful
open-source intelligence (OSINT) framework. Recon can swiftly gather intelligence and analyze for
vulnerabilities on a wide range of targets, sourced from public and private databases.
Recon-ng – Web Reconnaissance Framework
https://github.com/lanmaster53/recon-ng
Recon-ng is an incredibly powerful tool for Open Source Intelligence Gathering (OSINT).
Shodan
https://www.shodan.io/
Shodan focuses on the deep web and is considered a network security monitor. Shodan can index virtually
anything on the net. You can access data from phones, smart TV’s medical devices, webcams and more.
TheHarvester
https://tools.kali.org/information-gathering/theharvester
TheHarvester is an open-source intelligence tool that collects information based on specific targets. It
mostly deals with emails and domain information
AutoOSINT
https://github.com/bharshbarger/AutOSINT
datasploit
https://github.com/DataSploit/datasploit
An #OSINT Framework to perform various recon techniques on Companies, People, Phone Number, Bitcoin
Addresses, etc., aggregate all the raw data, and give data in multiple formats.
Inquisitor
https://github.com/penafieljlm/inquisitor
Opinionated organization-centric OSINT footprinting inspired from recon-ng and Maltego
